From: i***************3@gmail.com
To: CRAWLER
Time: 2023-04-14 19:25:14
SUBJECT:   I write to seek your coopera
  I write to seek your cooperation as my foreign partner and your
assistance to enable me to own properties and invest in the economy of
your country.
I apologize if this letter does not suit your personal or business
ethics, I came to know you in my Private Search after my fasting and
prayers, then I made up my mind to confide this confidential business
suggestion to you as a reliable and reputable person to handle this
confidential transaction.
My name is Ifeanyi Ezeobi, I work in an Oil and Gas Company. I made a
fixed deposit of $21.8 M in California Bank & Trust USA which I would
like to use the funds to invest in your country or any other good
country because of the unstable economy of our nation.
Please do let me know if you would like to partner with me to receive
the fund from California Bank & Trust USA for fruitful investment in
your country, if you would like to assist me as a partner then
indicate your interest after which we shall both discuss the
modalities and the sharing percentage.
All other information to facilitate the remittance of the funds will
be revealed to you in due course, if you are not interested, please
also indicate so, so that it will enable me to contact other foreign
partners who might be interested to work with me.
A swift acknowledgment of the receipt of this letter and early
establishment of position will be appreciated.
Call for your interest or whatsApp me on this number: +234-818 331 7195.
I am waiting for your reply.
Best regards,
Ifeanyi Ezeobi   
From: i***************3@gmail.com
To: cx12135@l******s.email
Time: 2023-04-14 20:37:44
SUBJECT: Re: I write to seek your coopera
Thanks for your anticipated response, I am glad to hear from you.
Which investment do you wish for us to invest my funds in that will be
beneficial to both of us in your country? I think you should know
better than me because you know how your country works, and also I
will be glad if I can enter into any investment in your country.
To me I was thinking of Hotel Resort, Agricultural Plant or House
Management Condominium investment to invest my funds on in your
country.
But you are free to come up with any good suggestions for profitable
business that we can invest my funds in, all what I need from you is
your cooperation as a foreigner and also stand to be my foreign
business partner investor by helping to handle the funds carefully in
your country.
Therefore I decided to establish any investment project title we may
agree together and everlasting lifetime partnership contact with you
as a citizen for more protection and proper supervision.
You will handle this investment project, I will enhance these Funds
into your care in a mutual agreement to work together and accept the
fact of being my international investor and business partner.
You have to bear in mind that this venture requires mutual trust and
understanding.
All my effort is to invest in a foreign country for maximum security
reasons. Above all, let me know how many percentage offers (% you
would like to collect from the total Funds as your compensation for
helping me, I have no choice than to take a chance. I will be
interested to invest into other viable ventures of your suggestion.
Please provide below to enable us proceed.
Name...
Address...
Phone Number....
Thanks for your anticipated cooperation.
Regards
Ifeanyi Ezeobi
